<keyLead id="DF0495F8650E047D2A866CB4FA3ADCD9" box="[151,1436,213,235]" pageId="15" pageNumber="264">1. Insemination duct entrance anterior to spermatheca and insemination duct forms a median loop beside the spermatheca.... 2</keyLead>
