<keyLead id="DF0495F8650E047D2AB26C91FA3ADD3A" box="[163,1436,243,265]" pageId="15" pageNumber="264">– Insemination duct entrance beside spermatheca, and insemination duct with no median loop beside the spermatheca...... 3</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
