<keyLead id="DF0495F8650E047D2A866DE7FA3ADDA9" box="[151,1436,389,411]" pageId="15" pageNumber="264">3. Left insemination duct (in ventral view) makes a full clockwise spiral coil prior to joining spermatheca................. 4</keyLead>
</paragraph>
