<keyLead id="DF0495F8650E047D2AB26D99FA3ADE22" box="[163,1436,507,529]" pageId="15" pageNumber="264">
– Spermatheca pear-shaped with spiral in the seminal duct hidden under the spermatheca (in ventral view)....... 
